Class CartesianProductSupplier

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.beryx.streamplify.product.CartesianProductSupplier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IntArraySupplier
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CartesianProductSupplier.BigInt, CartesianProductSupplier.Long

    public abstract class CartesianProductSupplier
extends java.lang.Object
implements IntArraySupplier
    A value supplier for cartesian product.
    It may compute the next tuple based on the current one, or by unranking an index.
